---
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>sugargeng</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="sugargeng 的个人主页，记录 AI 时代的软件工程、AI 应用开发、开发者工具和长期成长。"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <header class="nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">sugargeng</a>
        <nav>
          <a href="#writing">Writing</a>
          <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/sugargeng" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Developer · Builder · AI Explorer</p>
        <h1>A builder in the AI-native era.</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          我关注软件工程、AI 应用、开发者工具，以及如何把想法做成真正可用的产品。
          这里会记录我的技术探索、项目复盘和长期成长。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="writing" class="section">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="label">Writing</p>
          <h2>Notes on engineering, AI, and building.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <p class="card-label">AI Application</p>
            <h3>AI 应用开发</h3>
            <p>
              关注 Agentic Workflow、Tool Calling、RAG、模型评测、可观测性和工程稳定性。
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <p class="card-label">Engineering</p>
            <h3>软件工程</h3>
            <p>
              记录后端工程、系统设计、部署运维、可维护性和真实项目里的技术取舍。
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <p class="card-label">Growth</p>
            <h3>长期成长</h3>
            <p>
              思考 AI 时代的学习方式、个人知识系统、职业选择和持续创造。
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="projects" class="section">
        <div class="section-head">
          <p class="label">Projects</p>
          <h2>Selected work will be added here.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="card muted">
          <h3>Project notes are being curated.</h3>
          <p>
            我会在这里放置适合公开展示的项目、实验和开源作品。部分商业项目和私有项目不会公开展示。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-family:
      Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
      "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.16), transparent 34rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.12), transparent 32rem),
      #0b1020;
    color: #e5e7eb;
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1080px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 0 96px;
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 112px;
  }

  .brand {
    color: #f8fafc;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .nav nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .nav a {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav a:hover {
    color: #f8fafc;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    color: #93c5fd;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 820px;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 112px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.075em;
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .section {
    margin-top: 96px;
  }

  .section-head {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .label {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #93c5fd;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 26px;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.72);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
  }

  .card-label {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h3 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .muted {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .container {
      width: min(100% - 28px, 1080px);
      padding-top: 24px;
    }

    .nav {
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .nav nav {
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(48px, 18vw, 72px);
    }
  }
</style>
